---
title: Macaroni in a Creamy Tomato Sauce with Pancetta and Spinach
description: Everyone knows that in order to make great pasta, you’ve got to make a great sauce, too. But while the pasta part is a cinch for anyone who can boil water, the sauce part requires a bit more strategy. Luckily, we’re here to lead the way: we’re making a tomato cream sauce that’s as timeless as can be, thickening it with a roux (that’s a fancy term for a flour and butter base). It clings to macaroni's curves, giving you tangy, dairy-rich goodness with each bite.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/macaroni-in-a-creamy-tomato-sauce-37455597.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/wonder-ful-pasta-in-tomato-cream-sauce-5a1458297cc0c120da654d72-7876482f.pdf
